snippet.textDisplay:
One of the cringiest thing I have heard in my life. I guess this is where you literally choke the shit out of Bangla Music. Wanna be Pakistani coke studio, an wanna be Eva Baloch... Her picked up name is not even right, I know that there's no grammatical mistake for names but that words are not even right... Daughter of costal, wadda heck... I have been following her ever since she's been trying to do some music, I saw no improvements, no creativity, just her wanna be shits... I guess that is all they need to do top level music in this country... By all means I don't mean to be discouraging but at this highest level this is nothing but garbage.. wannabes at their best. 
They don't represent our music, culture or QUALITY. And surely they can't take criticisms.
